description:
PmEventSigM: Table containing performance management event signaling information for each cell, including timestamp, area, cell ID, and Ericsson-specific attributes.

dateTime: Timestamp of the event.
Area_Name: Name of the geographical area where the cell is located.
CellId: Unique identifier of the cell.
Id2: Redundant cell identifier (appears to be a duplicate of CellId).
Id3:  An identifier of unknown purpose (likely a counter or flag).
vsDataType:  Specifies the data type as performance management event signaling.
vsDataFormatVersion: Specifies the version of the Ericsson-specific attributes format.
PmEventSigM.userLabel: User-defined label (currently empty).
PmEventSigM.pmEventSigMId: Unique identifier for each event record.
